          "author": "rohanmahy",
          "authorAssociation": "CONTRIBUTOR",
          "body": "I reserved these (first for adopted WG items, then in order of original publication) for all MLS drafts with a component id:\r\n- 0x0006 `apq_info` - PQ combiners draft\r\n- 0x0007 `associated_parties` - associated parties draft\r\n- 0x0008 `external_receivers` - semiprivate message draft\r\n- 0x0009 `key_package_core_hash` - this draft\r\n- 0x000A `root_private_signature_key` - private external messages draft\r\n- 0x000B `external_encryption_public_key` - private external messages draft",
